Senior Recruitment Consultant - Healthcare ServicesPlum Jobs – Dubai
ResponsibilitiesSourcing new business opportunities in the healthcare industryRecruitment of medical / healthcare professionals as per the clients’ specificationsSourcing of candidates through social media, database searches, networking and traditional recruitment methodsEnsuring that all the certificates and documentation are compliant with the requirements for the roles and clients
Essential Skills & Experience Required8 – 10 years in a head hunting or recruitment consultancyA minimum of 2 – 3 years recruitment consultancy / headhunting experience in the Gulf regionFluency in English is essentialProven ability in business development
EducationBachelors Degree
Candidate ProfileAged between 30 – 40 yearsUAE / GCC driving licenseArabic or Western nationality
